{
  "stem": "23730.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we had to leave Hanover.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The camp was bombed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, the camp was bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the surroundings was bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to leave Hanover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were needed in Hildesheim, because the railway station in Hildesheim was bombed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to go and work there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are taken there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Hildesheim, there was not a real concentration camp, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was probably [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Zurich ?] already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The, the National Theater was made into a camp, which was terrible, if you think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A beautiful, lovely place, torn into pieces by us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then came the Allied bombing of, of Hildesheim on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was the 11th of February.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were all running towards the outskirts of Hildesheim, because it was obvious the city was condemned to die-- to be destroyed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could see it, this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the whole population was running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole population was running towards the cemeteries and towards the outskirts of the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you could already hear the fantastic noise of the bombing-- the bombers coming nearer to the city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was undescribable-- fantastic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then my famous incident-- how stupid one can be if you are German and you are commanded to do something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you are  brainwashed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Can you-- I give you a scenario.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Already, the, the bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The population of the city were running, and screaming, and shouting towards the outskirts, right, to get away from the bombing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So were we.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And  in the confusion, some of us went onto the pavement, certainly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there is a German young soldier standing there on one leg with two crutches.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he shouts-- [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I, I said to him, you idiot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He looked at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
